oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dottie West, Red Sovine, and Rex Allen Jr.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Allen, Rex, 1947-; Offset printing; Sovine, Red; West, Dottie, 1932-1991;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising The Dottie West Show starring Dottie West and Cross Country with Red Sovine and Rex Allen, Jr. The negative that would have contained information on the talent agency is missing. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
